## Get Liquidate Collateral Status

<%= partial "includes/APIReference/Lending/Examples/get_liquidation_transaction_status.tmpl.erb" %>

Retrieves status of a liquidation transaction creation request.

<aside class="success">Pro Tip: For best results, poll this API no more frequently than every 1000ms.</aside>

### HTTP Request

<img src="images/get.png" alt="get" class="http_verb"/> <api>`https://api.example.com/v1/lending/loans/<ID>/transactions/status?handlerId=<value>`</api>

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
ID | The ID of the loan for which to retrieve transaction status	

### Query Parameters

Parameter | Use | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
handlerId | required | The identifier from the results of the liquidation transaction creation request

### Response Properties

Property | Description | Notes
--------- | ------- | -------
status | The status of the liquidation transaction request | One of: <em>PENDING</em>, <em>COMPLETE</em>, or <em>FAILED</em>
reason | Detailed explanation for the status | Set only when status is <em>FAILED</em>
transaction | The newly created object | Set only when status is <em>COMPLETE</em>

